                          ────■ DESCRiPTiON ■────


 Drug Bust is a fast paced factual observational series that follows New Zealand's largest police district,
 Counties Manukau as they fight the war against drugs.

 The district has the highest population in New Zealand but it is also one of the poorest regions - and with
 this comes crime. With unprecedented access we follow the district's crack investigation teams as they
 take on the criminal underworld in a fight to take back their communities.


                                                                        
